&lt;h2&gt;Core Mission&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build and maintain GenAI-powered tools and pipelines that enable the Design and Sales teams to work faster, smarter, and more creatively -- with Anthropic Claude and complementary GenAI platforms as active capabilities in their day-to-day workflows while serving as an AI educator and bridge between the DWI team and the design organization.&lt;/p&gt;
