&lt;li&gt;Building and iterating on GenAI image and rendering tools for design workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting the AI-assisted product creation pipeline (CAD-to-flat-lay, on-model rendering)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leveraging Anthropic Claude for design workflow automation and AI-assisted processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining and evolving existing GenAI tools built for internal design use&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with Design and Sales stakeholders to identify new AI workflow opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educating and enabling Design and Sales team members on AI tools and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bridging the technology and AI gap between the DWI team and the design organization&lt;/li&gt;
