&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;That&#39;s the FAM Brands difference.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;377&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;The Director of Quality Assurance at Fam Brands is responsible for building, leading, and continuously improving a best-in-class quality program that protects our brands, our customers, and our consumers. This role oversees all quality assurance activities across product development, sourcing, production, and distribution to ensure that all products consistently meet or exceed internal standards, regulatory requirements and customer expectations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;377&quot;&gt;You will play a pivotal role in ensuring our products meet the highest standards of quality, safety, and regulatory compliance. This leadership position involves overseeing quality assurance processes, managing compliance initiatives and collaborating with cross-functional teams to uphold our commitment to excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Strategy &amp;amp; Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Develop and execute a comprehensive quality assurance strategy aligned with Fam Brands’ business objectives and growth plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Establish, communicate, and maintain quality vision, policies, and standards across the organization and supply base.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop a high-performing QA team across multiple locations and time zones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Influence senior leadership on quality-related risk, trade-offs and investment priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Management Systems&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Design, implement, and maintain an integrated Quality Management System (QMS) that supports consistent, repeatable product quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Define and standardize QA processes, procedures, and documentation for product development, fit, testing, inspections and release.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Ensure compliance with all applicable regulatory, safety and industry standards for relevant product categories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Continuously assess and improve QA tools, systems and technology platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product &amp;amp; Supplier Quality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Set product quality standards and technical requirements (e.g., specifications, tolerances, performance criteria) in partnership with Product Development, Design and Production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;Develop and manage supplier quality programs, including qualification, audits, scorecards and corrective action requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
